<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 01:11:13 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>Jack Dorsey：现在每个公司都可以成为迷你 AGI</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/jack-dorsey-every-company-can-now-be-a-mini-agi</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 01:11:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/jack-dorsey-every-company-can-now-be-a-mini-agi</guid></item><item><title>植物的决策揭示了哪些智慧</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/what-a-plants-decision-making-reveals-about-intelligence</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 00:56:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/what-a-plants-decision-making-reveals-about-intelligence</guid></item><item><title>无需电池：单个有机器件可以充当室内太阳能电池和光电探测器</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/no-battery-needed-single-organic-device-can-act-as-both-indoor-solar-cell-and-photodetector</link><description>下一代光电系统（将光能转换为电能的设备）利用基于有机半导体的室内能源自主架构来实现尖端应用。值得注意的是，有机半导体具有机械灵活性、溶液加工性和带隙可调光电特性，使其在通过有机光伏（OPV）进行室内发电以及通过有机光电探测器（OPD）进行光谱选择性光电探测方面具有很高的利润。不幸的是，OPV 和 OPD 领域取得的技术进步很大程度上是分开的，因此需要进一步研究开发用于同时进行能量收集和光电检测的双功能 OPV-OPD 系统。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/no-battery-needed-single-organic-device-can-act-as-both-indoor-solar-cell-and-photodetector2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 00:41:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/no-battery-needed-single-organic-device-can-act-as-both-indoor-solar-cell-and-photodetector</guid></item><item><title>科学家破解黄金形成背后的20年核谜团</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/scientists-crack-a-20-year-nuclear-mystery-behind-the-creation-of-gold</link><description>直到某些不稳定的原子核分裂后，金才能形成。这些核转变究竟是如何展开的长期以来一直很难确定。现在，田纳西大学 (UT) 的核物理学家在一项研究中报告了三项发现，阐明了这一过程的重要部分。他们的发现可以帮助研究人员建立改进的恒星事件模型，这些恒星事件会产生重元素，并更好地预测奇异原子核的行为。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-crack-a-20-year-nuclear-mystery-behind-the-creation-of-gold.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 00:26:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/scientists-crack-a-20-year-nuclear-mystery-behind-the-creation-of-gold</guid></item><item><title>结束太阳的垄断：仿星器聚变的未来 — Brian Berzin，Thea Energy 首席执行官</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/ending-the-suns-monopoly-the-future-of-stellarator-fusion-brian-berzin-ceo-thea-energy</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 Apr 2026 00:11:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/ending-the-suns-monopoly-the-future-of-stellarator-fusion-brian-berzin-ceo-thea-energy</guid></item><item><title>构建再生医学的未来</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/building-the-future-of-regenerative-medicine</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Apr 2026 23:56:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/building-the-future-of-regenerative-medicine</guid></item><item><title>GLP-1 受体激动剂</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/glp-1-receptor-agonists</link><description>胰高血糖素样肽-1 (GLP-1) 受体激动剂是肠促胰岛素类似物，可促进葡萄糖介导的胰岛素释放，用于治疗 2 型糖尿病和肥胖症。 GLP-1 受体激动剂以及 GLP-1 和葡萄糖依赖性促胰岛素肽激动剂具有多种作用机制，包括减少胃排空、抑制胰高血糖素分泌、有益改变肠道微生物群，以及直接影响下丘脑核团以增强饱腹感（促进减肥）。除了 GLP-1 受体激动剂对血糖水平和体重产生令人印象深刻的影响外，大规模随机对照试验还表明，GLP-1 受体激动剂可降低高危人群和 2 型糖尿病患者的心血管风险并减缓进展为肾功能衰竭。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/glp-1-receptor-agonists.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Apr 2026 23:41:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/glp-1-receptor-agonists</guid></item><item><title>&amp;#39;你的薪水是多少？我告诉他，他说没问题，我们加倍。那些日子已经一去不复返了：听游戏开发传奇人物回忆 1989 年已经结束的“电脑游戏的黄金时代”是一次旅行</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/whats-your-salary-i-told-him-and-he-said-no-problem-well-double-and-those-days-are-gone-listening-to-game-dev-legends-reminiscing-in-1989-about-the-go</link><description>这就像我们说“还记得 2016 年的美好时光吗？” &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/whats-your-salary-i-told-him-and-he-said-no-problem-well-double-and-those-days-are-gone-listening-to-game-dev-legends-reminiscing-in-1989-about-the-go2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Apr 2026 23:26:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/whats-your-salary-i-told-him-and-he-said-no-problem-well-double-and-those-days-are-gone-listening-to-game-dev-legends-reminiscing-in-1989-about-the-go</guid></item><item><title>《我的世界》创作者 Notch 表示“DLSS 根本上毫无意义”，但 X 评论却说“嗯，实际上”</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/minecraft-creator-notch-says-dlss-fundamentally-makes-no-sense-but-the-x-comments-say-um-actually</link><description>我想你不必同意它。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/minecraft-creator-notch-says-dlss-fundamentally-makes-no-sense-but-the-x-comments-say-um-actually2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Apr 2026 23:11:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/minecraft-creator-notch-says-dlss-fundamentally-makes-no-sense-but-the-x-comments-say-um-actually</guid></item><item><title>索尼收购机器学习公司 Cinemersive Labs</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/sony-acquires-machine-learning-company-cinemersive-labs</link><description>其团队将加入索尼的研发部门视觉计算小组。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/sony-acquires-machine-learning-company-cinemersive-labs2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Apr 2026 22:56:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/sony-acquires-machine-learning-company-cinemersive-labs</guid></item></channe